data.text: Perry is a song/songwriter. She started taking singing lessons around 9 years old and played guitar when she was 13 years old. Katy graduated from Dos Pueblos High school. Both her parents were pastors . Her and her siblings were not allowed to listen to rock or music that they did not approve of. As a teen Katy then became rebellion and got piercings. Perry became interested in music .
